Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做克勞德˙肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠揭發『魔石索沙』所隱藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便和蕾娜開始朝著艾爾大陸前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少用你們那雙髒手隨便碰我!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來在途中遇到了紋章術師塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和一個叫做艾修頓的劍客變成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體內沈睡紅蓮之火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉火王派蒙之名解放你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請依聖三角的引導
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將站在我眼前的愚昧者，給予灼熱的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要離開阿利亞村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還跟那兩個傢伙一起旅行呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在找魔石索沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和克勞德為了調查魔石索沙的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須到艾爾大陸去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我聽說魔石索沙帶來的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本超乎我們的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼還會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這塊大地－艾克斯貝爾受到欺凌民不聊生之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便會出現一位異國打扮的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者高舉著光劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救苦難的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德就是傳說中的這位勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友…啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了幫他們尋寶和驅魔，雖然多繞了一點遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過折騰了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算到達了克洛斯大陸東部的港灣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是哈利啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡熱熱鬧鬧的，挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海風吹起來也好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把謎底解開…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事啊我們待會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先找間旅館好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了每天餐風露宿的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好餓、背酸得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭發乾燥，皮膚也快乾死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也對耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒用的劍客到底跑到哪裡去了嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(來看一看啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(新到的貨色哪)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我這裡的貨色最齊全哪)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請問你，到底要摸到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你們的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把他弄走好不好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這是克洛斯l3世紀的橡木桶欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種遙遠又古老的香味…\N你一定裝過白蘭地對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香，聞到我都快要醉倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛剛到現在就是這樣沒離開過耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他該不會是個…迷戀酒桶的收集狂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼收集狂啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上有這種人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賣你們5000弗爾就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很貴嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要買啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真的要揹著這個大酒桶去艾爾大陸啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要傻了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾修頓他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠們都在向你求救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…就買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個酒桶該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25午前在卡利亞工房限量生產的…檜木酒桶吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小長和小圓不會有什麼事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經把塞麗奴的帽子掛在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該很快就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像他那種人啊…為他擔心根本是多餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣倒也罷了，要是迷路的話怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯國王給我們的通行証\N能不能借給我看看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…哪裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…看不到海了耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們…是迷路啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想休息的時候，我們去看要搭的船吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是，我們馬上就要過海了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是得整頓一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲…有沒有搞錯啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿腫得這麼厲害好慘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又來了，那妳先等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去拿一些熱水來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感激妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~喂~喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，眼睛突然有一點刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是灰塵跑進去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是睫毛長反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳最好不要揉得太用力，我來幫妳看一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴姐也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，她的紋章術會幫上克勞德不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不要計較這些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴姐，熱水…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜、蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~太好了…碰上好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也聽到蕾娜說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才，從她站的位置看起來，也難怪她會誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差那麼多…不會吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…竟然接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆個搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道一定是妳，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪，我們能在這裡碰面還真是巧耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…我們離山越來越近了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是方向…好像錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼啊你?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把房間鑰匙通通都交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兄弟要到你這裡來找樣寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳下次再來捧場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…蕾娜，妳會不會吃得太多啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土產吃太多肚子會脹耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂，我要全部吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃東西的時候不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，喝點水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德也太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這件事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己說這趟旅行可能要豁出性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還做出那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要繼續不停的吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀蕾娜 好了啦!妳冷靜一點  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳放手，放手放手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼『整頓一下心情』嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我才不要跟著他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就讓我繼續吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦，不要鬧了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是克勞德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不像是這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼看到的不可能錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…妳要回阿利亞村嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不想跟他一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡也不是辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點，先溜為妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德在裡面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，明明是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那是我的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，快溜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，把我的包包還我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，妳追去太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是通行証在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強盜、有強盜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是小雪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些待會再說!蕾娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想念妳啊…妳好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你的樣子好像不怎麼好哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了一件大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把包包還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人還不死心啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見這裡面的東西很重要欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它還給我、還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不還
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，通行證…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，快抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…破…斬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德、克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行証…被人偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不能怪妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事都要怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為塞麗奴姐人那麼好，長得又好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我誤會了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妳…誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼…在意克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛才還真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快把它解決掉吧，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?我怎麼會在這個地方啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都在?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦?看來你們又合好了嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是通行證…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們三個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還蠻滿意我天雷電波的威力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，塞麗奴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行證又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我一邊賣果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊尋找有哪家店願意請我去唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌手…好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡唱歌\N人活著總要誠實的面對自己嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，蕾娜也是一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼?船長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不肯開船呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有聽到那個傳聞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一片大海已經不是我們認識的大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到魔石的影響，它平就變得不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連大海也…改變了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是魔石索沙的影響嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙…
